    public class PeerPressureVertexProgramDefinition
extends Object
implements IVertexProgramDefinition<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.computer.clustering.peerpressure.PeerPressureVertexProgram>
    GridGraph specific vertex program definition for PeerPressureVertexProgram.
    This class maintains any extra data, like dynamic property, needed by GridGraph to support graph computing peer pressure algorithm.
    Author:
    guobao.chen
